fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 declined 93.65 points or 0.48% to settle at 19,253.80. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, advanced 2.22% to 12.06. HDFC Bank, Reliance Industries and ICICI Bank were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The September 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 28 September 2023.
